info.name: Compass Ottoman
info.LongDescription:
Inspired by a Middle Eastern design, this Compass ottoman is covered in high-quality leather and features a geometric pattern on the seat detailed by twin-needle topstitching and piping down each side panel as well as around the circumference. Available in tan, this beautiful low ottoman is a comfortable seat and footstool, and also doubles as a handy spot to put a laptop or food tray.

“The Compass ottoman is not just a statement piece, it’s also an incredibly comfortable footstool.” Freedom furniture buyer.
